    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/vad-cou2-not-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors assessed; all show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors not assessed, representing unquantified epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed but input distributions not device-specific. The mesh-independence claim is registered and considered supportive of numerical adequacy, and available evidence from the grid convergence study and hemolysis benchmark provides contextual confidence; however, the structured provenance linkage from that claim to the underlying evidence records has not been formally completed in this package. Overall credibility is insufficient for a Class III VAD submission at MRL 5. Decision: Accepted for internal review stage only pending remediation of all gap factors.",
